Jawas2: The Revengining


Summary:

Jawas is a minimalistic Web Application Server Platform.
This project is a complete rewrite of the Jawas platform.  

Goals:

1.) Smaller <1k lines of code
2.) Faster by removing everything unnecessary
3.) Distributed support for clusters of servers
4.) More HTTP method support: GET, PUT, POST, DELETE, etc.
5.) Cleaner module system.

Status:

v0.0.1 - Basic startup & connection monitoring working 148 LOC, 73 statements.

Dave Goehrig


